properties.areaDesc: Currituck Sound; Coastal waters from NC VA border to Currituck Beach Light NC out 20 nm
properties.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued January 13 at 6:07AM EST until January 13 at 4:00PM EST by NWS Wakefield VA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Dense fog will reduce visibility to 1/2 NM or less.

* WHERE...Currituck Sound and Coastal waters from NC VA border
to Currituck Beach Light NC out 20 nm.

* WHEN...Until 4 PM EST this afternoon.

* IMPACTS...Low visibility will make navigation difficult.
properties.instruction:
If you must navigate, proceed with caution. Use proper fog signals.
Make sure all running lights are on. Remember to use your radar and
compass.

NWSheadline: DENSE FOG ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 4 PM EST THIS AFTERNOON
